  "summaries": [
    {
      "id": 5696,
      "category": "team",
      "content": "User uploaded text files can be linked from external websites and end up appearing in search engine result pages if you perform a search such as: `site:*.irccloud-cdn.com ext:txt`\n\nIt's not possible to completely prevent such listings on all search engines, but some search crawlers support the `X-Robots-Tag` header which can be used to indicate indexing is disallowed.\n\nThis header was added as a result of this report.",
